author: Inside Edition
description: Country song "Walk My Walk" by singer Breaking Rust is number one on the country digital song sales chart. However, the singer and the song are all AI-generated. It’s been streamed 2.1 million times on Spotify, and 11.5 million times on YouTube. It is sparking a huge debate. Inside Edition demonstrates how easy it is to create a song generated entirely by artificial intelligence using the AI music program Suno.
title: Country Song Hit 'Walk My Walk' Entirely Generated by AI

author: Inside Edition
description: The neighbor who was saved from a naked man by her 79-year-old landlord is speaking out. The naked man stormed to Chloe Dzielak's front door and she tells Inside Edition he started yelling at her. Dzielak says she ran out of her home and started screaming. Landlord George Karkoc heard her cries for help and grabbed his gun. He rushed out to find himself under physical assault. War veteran Karkoc credits his military training for helping save both their lives.
title: Woman Saved From Naked Man By Her Landlord Speaks Out

author: Inside Edition
description: “Smallville” actress Allison Mack's career took a nose dive after she joined a sex cult and recruited young women for its depraved leader Keith Raniere. Now, Mack is speaking out for the first time about her role in the notorious cult known as NXIVM. Court documents show that women recruited into NXIVM were branded and turned into sex slaves for the pleasure of their cult leader. Mack spoke out on a seven-part podcast "Allison After NXIVM."
title: Allison Mack Reveals Her Role In NXIVM Sex Cult For The 1st Time

author: Inside Edition
description: Heart-stopping video shows a 3-year-old girl wandering into a swimming pool before slipping into deeper water and starting to drown. Suddenly, Robert Grillo, the little girl's cousin, jumped into the pool. Little Emilia had just finished a swimming lesson at her Miami home with a private instructor 15 minutes earlier. Emilia was back swimming the next day. She and her mother Bethany Rodriguez spoke with Inside Edition. Emilia thanks her big cousin for saving her.
title: Drowning Toddler Rescued From Pool Minutes After Swimming Lesson

author: Inside Edition
description: A police officer found a home in flames. His bodycam footage captured the inferno and the chilling cries coming from inside. Auburn, New York, Officer Paul Flickner and a deputy sheriff successfully helped the victim escape through the window. Flickner, hailed as a hero, spoke with Inside Edition. The family tells Inside Edition that they survived another big fire in the same home four years ago.
title: Bodycam Shows Police Officer Rescuing Victim From House Fire

author: Inside Edition
description: Jimmy Kimmel broke down in tears with a heartfelt tribute after announcing the death of his band leader and best friend Cleto Escobedo III. Kimmel and Escobedo have known each other since he was 9 and became inseparable. When Kimmel landed his late night show in 2002, he wanted Escobedo to lead the late night band. Escobedo has been absent from the show for several months. Published reports say that he died from complications after a liver transplant. He was 59.
title: Jimmy Kimmel Honors His Friend and Band Leader, Cleto Escobedo III

author: Inside Edition
description: The Housekeeping Olympics is taking place in Las Vegas, Nevada, for its 35th year. Teams snag trophies and gold medals, but it is mostly about bragging rights for some of the hardest working people in Las Vegas.
title: Housekeeping Olympics Held In Las Vegas #shorts

author: Inside Edition
description: It's been more than 90 years since an infamous couple's crime spree came to a violent end, but the legend of Bonnie Parker and Clyde Barrow lives on as something of a love story. A town in Iowa is trying to hold on to its part in their story. The town of Stuart, population just under 2,000, takes pride in this site of an old bank that was once robbed by the ill-fated duo. Many were afraid it might be demolished. Inside Edition Digital’s Mara Montalbano has more.
title: Old Bank Building, Once Robbed By Bonnie and Clyde, Getting A Facelift

author: Inside Edition
description: A naked man ran across a neighborhood street and confronted residents when things turned violent. The landlord, Vietnam War veteran George Karkoc, says he heard his female neighbor scream for help so he grabbed his gun for protection and ran to help.
title: Veteran Describes Deadly Confrontation With Naked Intruder #shorts

author: Inside Edition
description: This customer must have seemed harmless limping into a bank with a cane and a neck brace, but cops say it was all an act. Police in Slidell, Louisiana, released this video of the suspect who they say limped up to a teller, handed them a note and then started shouting, "This is a robbery". They say the suspect also demanded money and then walked out of the bank without limping. Inside Edition Digital’s Mara Montalbano has more.
title: Limping Man Robs Louisiana Bank Then Runs Away: Cops

author: Inside Edition
description: The Johnson family from Waukee, Iowa, turned its front porch into a food pantry donation site – and donations are booming.
title: Family Turns Front Porch Into Thriving Food Pantry #shorts

author: Inside Edition
description: An obsessed stalker victimized actress Eva LaRue and her daughter Kaya for 12 years. Chilling letters to LaRue were signed "Freddy Krueger," the disfigured killer from "Nightmare on Elm Street."
title: Eva LaRue Opens Up About Being Stalked For Over A Decade #shorts

author: Inside Edition
description: A popular food influencer has died, according to his talent agency. Michael Duarte was known to his millions of followers as FoodWithBearHands. He amassed a large fan base with his over-the-top recipes. Many of them included ingredients that were not for picky eaters, like frogs legs. Inside Edition Digital’s Mara Montalbano has more.
title: Influencer FoodWithBearHands, Michael Duarte, Dies in 'Horrible Incident'

author: Inside Edition
description: The black, pointy, wide-brimmed hat worn by Margaret Hamilton – aka the Wicked Witch of the West – will soon be up for grabs, courtesy of Heritage Auctions.
title: Wicked Witch Of The West's Hat Can Be Yours #shorts
